msgid ""
"[skull]: -X. X is 2 more than the current Storm Intensity.\n"
"[cultist]: -6. Place 1 doom on the nearest enemy.\n"
"[tablet]: -2 for each open sky adjacent to your current location.\n"
"[elder_thing]: -4. If there is an enemy at your location, reveal another token."
msgstr ""
"[skull]：–X。X为当前风暴强度+2。"
"[cultist]：–6。在最近的敌人上放置1个毁灭标记。"
"[tablet]：每有一张天空与你当前地点相邻，–2。"
